    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Browser Wars: Is your browser prepared for HTML5 ?]]></title>
    <link href="http://parasnarang.github.io/blog/blog/2010/12/22/browser-wars-is-your-browser-prepared/"/>
    <updated>2010-12-22T04:36:00+05:30</updated>
    <id>http://parasnarang.github.io/blog/blog/2010/12/22/browser-wars-is-your-browser-prepared</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class='post'>
<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML5"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">HTML5</span></a></b><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">&nbsp;is going to be the next big thing! It is</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">currently under development and will be&nbsp;</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">the next major revision of the HTML&nbsp;standard.&nbsp;</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">W3C and WHATWG are currently working on its development.&nbsp;</span></span><br /><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span><br /><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">Basically it is going to make life very easy, both for developers as well as end users. Once HTML5 is approved, there wont be any need of&nbsp;proprietary players or of Flash, Silverlight etc. All the media will be a normal part of the webpage. Notable examples of HTML5 are TweetDeck app for Google Chrome,&nbsp;YouTube's&nbsp;HTML5 videos site.&nbsp;</span></span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">Adobe html5 pack for dreamweaver has been released. Apple.com also has a HTML5 page.</span></span><br /><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span><br /><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">I conducted the Html5 test using www.html5test.com on the current popular web browsers and the results are as follows:</span></span><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">(Operating System: Windows 7 64-bit)</span></span></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">Firefox 4 beta 7:</span></span></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_99k5zlQdUsM/TRErwhc9gDI/AAAAAAAAAFs/xEuvy-QkAfw/s1600/firefox4beta7.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><img border="0" height="376" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_99k5zlQdUsM/TRErwhc9gDI/AAAAAAAAAFs/xEuvy-QkAfw/s640/firefox4beta7.jpg" width="640" /></span></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">Chrome 9 beta:</span></span></span></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_99k5zlQdUsM/TRErQ4cSQ4I/AAAAAAAAAFg/xqi_3p0l9aw/s1600/chrome9beta.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><img border="0" height="376" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_99k5zlQdUsM/TRErQ4cSQ4I/AAAAAAAAAFg/xqi_3p0l9aw/s640/chrome9beta.jpg" width="640" /></span></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span></span></div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 23px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;">Safari 5:</span></span><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="htt